{"service_name": "Protective Monitoring as a Service", "service_id": "5449990050676736", "company_name": "Mds Technologies Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Mds Technologies Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Protective Monitoring as a Service\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Protective Monitoring is designed to assist your organisation in meeting HMG Security Policy Framework requirements and CESG Good Practice Guide Number 13 for Protective Monitoring.The service is delivered as a managed cloud based Monitoring and Reporting Service and can also be run independently of your IT provider.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Customer gets a view of activity across their entire estate\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Fully Managed Third Party Solution\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     All logs are co llected and securely stored\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Baseline Service aligned with GPG13 Recording Profile A\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Deter Service aligned with GPG13 Recording Profile B\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Uses the Assuria Log Management (ALM) product\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Daily, weekly and monthly reporting\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Enhanced Situational Awareness\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     CESG CCTM Accredited solution\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Service delivered by UK company\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Customisable to meet specific accreditor interpretations of GPG13\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Massively scalable\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Forensically sound log collection and storage\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Collected and secured log data can be exported\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a32000 per instance per month\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Month\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92409/5449990050676736-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92409/5449990050676736-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92409/5449990050676736-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92409/5449990050676736-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n   